Parliament, Wednesday, 5 December 2018 – The Standing Committee on Public Accounts (Scopa) will this afternoon hold a hearing with the National Treasury on the Integrated Financial Management System (IFMS) forensic report. Details of meeting: Date: Wednesday, 5 December 2018
	Time: 18:00
	Venue: Committee Room E249, Second Floor, National Assembly Building ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES ON BEHALF OF THE CHAIRPERSON OF SCOPA, MR THEMBA GODI. For media enquiries, please contact the committee’s Media Officer: Name: Ms Faith Ndenze
